class.abstract: Interface to create an Edit Properties property page.

method.name: BuildEditor
method.abstract: Constructs the dialog objects of the editor.

method.abstract: Cancels a modification when closing the panel.

method.abstract: Closes dialog object open by the editor.

class.name: CATISearchInformation
